{
  "id": "adv_event_2310_01_05",
  "title": "スーパー\nナイスな\ntwins",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "今思えば、最初のユニットコンセプトの話し合いの\n時点ですれ違いが生じていましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I think about it‚ we were already on different pages\nfrom the very first discussion about the unit concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.840703106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんと芽衣の中で『かっこいい』がどんなのか\n微妙に違ってた……ってことだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It means that our image of “coolness” was\nslightly different… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0407032013,
      "endTime": 16.2549430848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "まず、私なんですが……大前提として\n芽衣の方がダンスの技術が高いと思っていますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To begin with‚ I…\nI believe that Mei is the more skilled dancer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4549431801,
      "endTime": 24.9751475334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、芽衣と組む以上は私が芽衣のポテンシャルを\n最大限に引き出そう……と考えていたんですのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I was thinking about drawing out Mei’s potential\nto the fullest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.181814162,
      "endTime": 34.3973472279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんの考え方はとっても嬉しいんだけどさ\nそれだと芽衣ばっかりやりやすくなっちゃわない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really happy you thought that way‚ Suzu-nyan‚\nbut would that make things too easy only for Mei!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5906805039,
      "endTime": 42.0470311167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私が芽衣のレベルに合わせて頑張ればいいだけですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just have to work hard to match Mei’s level!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2403643927,
      "endTime": 46.557821877900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、せっかく二人で頑張ろうって言ってたのに\nすずにゃんばっかり頑張ることになっちゃう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we said we’d work hard together‚\nand now you’re going to be the only one struggling!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7578218779,
      "endTime": 53.540971883299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……確かに……ただ芽衣のことばかり\n考えているとそうなってしまいますわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… You’re right… I guess when I only focus on Mei‚\nthat’s what happens…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7209724111,
      "endTime": 62.740972678199995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、芽衣はね、すずにゃんと芽衣が持っている\n二人のいいところといいところをくっつけたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Mei was thinking… If we combined\nour good points together‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9476393066,
      "endTime": 70.9374381386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もっといいものになるんじゃないかなって思ってたの\nだから、『かっこ可愛い感じ』にしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we could make something even better.\nThat’s why I went for a “cool and cute” vibe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1107721332,
      "endTime": 77.7731259351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私達二人のいいところ……なるほど、だから芽衣の案は\n可愛らしさも兼ね備えていたのですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The good points of both of us… I see‚ so that’s why your idea‚ Mei‚\nalso had a touch of cuteness to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9531264627,
      "endTime": 87.6264823282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことでしたら納得がいきますわ。芽衣、私達\n二人にしか作れない、最強のステージを作りますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand now. Mei‚ we’re going to\ncreate the greatest stage that only the two of us can make!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8131488805,
      "endTime": 97.4098836904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！\nそれじゃあさ、作詞も進めちゃわない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!\nSo‚ should we get started on the lyrics too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5832173989,
      "endTime": 101.4317222283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "それどころじゃない状態でしたものね……\nよーし、一気に作りますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were in no state to do that…\nAlright‚ let’s write them all in one go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5917226797,
      "endTime": 107.8199992184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "おー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0333326662,
      "endTime": 110.43333257079999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ、最初の打ち合わせで芽衣が話した\n「二人の大好きなものを一杯詰め込む」ってアイデア",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ remember what I said at our first meeting?\n“Let’s include lots of things we both love!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7800048157,
      "endTime": 119.5898934647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞に詰め込んじゃうのはどうかな？\n芽衣だと……ドーナツとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about we include those things in the lyrics?\nLike for Mei… Donuts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7698939924,
      "endTime": 126.06989399230001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツなら……英語も入れてみるのはいかが？\n例えば……「ドーナツ Eating!」とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s donuts… How about adding some English lyrics?\nLike… “Donut Eating!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2698941831,
      "endTime": 135.66406666080002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ～。さっすが英語ペラペラのすずにゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh~. As expected of the fluent English speaker‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8774000132,
      "endTime": 140.4873422587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、これでペラペラと言われるのは\nさすがに恥ずかしいですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a bit embarrassing\nto be called fluent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.6806755349,
      "endTime": 146.1677954957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんの大好きなものと言えば……\nポテトチップスは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about things you love‚ Suzu-nyan…\nPotato chips?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3611286764,
      "endTime": 152.5877048139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "言葉が長いから入れ辛いかもしれませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The word is too long‚ it might be hard to include.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7810380423,
      "endTime": 156.6023562396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "アウトロですずにゃんがポテトチップスを\nぱりぱり食べる音だけ入れてみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about we just put in the sound of Suzu-nyan\ncrunching on potato chips for outro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.769031092,
      "endTime": 161.55395159370002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな控えめなアウトロ、聞いたことがない\nですわよ……。というか恥ずかし過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve nev+I44:M45er heard of an outro that’s that understated…\nAnd it’s way too embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7539514983,
      "endTime": 168.6944978202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……私がこの曲に入れたいワードは……\nジェラシー、かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… A word I want to include in this song…\nJealousy‚ maybe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8211652562,
      "endTime": 177.3513011739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "じぇらしー？　なんでー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jealousy? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.5513013646,
      "endTime": 180.8355643079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "今回はことあるごとに芽衣にジェラシーを抱いて\n迷惑を掛けてしまいましたから……そのけじめですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’ve been jealous of you every step of the way this time‚ Mei‚\nand I’ve caused you a lot of trouble… It’s my way of making amends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.0222309077,
      "endTime": 189.4939313854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_05-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ～……すずにゃんかっこいい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh~… You’re so cool‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.6872646615,
      "endTime": 193.470593004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
